==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: maintenance man
<hw>maintenance man</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A worker, usually in an
enterprise or apartment building, whose job is to repair damaged parts
of a building or its fixtures, and sometimes to make improvements or
other changes to the building.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>maintenance staff</ent>⟦br⟧
